  "title": "ISic003454. I.Sicily inscription 003454",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Maria Barbieri</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>† <span data-text=\"Ένθάδε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">Ένθάδε</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"κὲτεκεῖται\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κὲτε</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰωά\n                    ννης μον\n                    αχὸς ὁ Με\n                    νουθ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰωά\n                    ννης\"><span data-text=\"Ἰωά\n                    ννης\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἰωάννης\">Ἰωά-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[νν]ης</span></span>  <span data-text=\"μον\n                    αχὸς\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"μοναχός\">μον-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[αχὸ]ς</span>  <span data-text=\"ὁ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ὁ</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Με\n                    νουθ\"><span data-text=\"Με\n                    νουθ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Μενουθ\">Με-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[νου]θ</span></span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. ΚῈΤΕκὲτε</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Ένθάδε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">Ένθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κὲτε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κὲτε</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἰωάννης\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἰωάννης\">Ἰωάννης</span>  <span data-text=\"μοναχὸς\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"μοναχός\">μοναχὸς</span>  <span data-text=\"ὁ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ὁ</span>  <span data-text=\"Μενουθ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Μενουθ\">Μενουθ</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Maria Barbieri</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>†<span data-text=\"Ένθάδε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"κὲτεκεῖται\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΕΤΕ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰωά\n                    ννης μον\n                    αχὸς ὁ Με\n                    νουθ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰωά\n                    ννης\"><span data-text=\"Ἰωά\n                    ννης\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἰωάννης\">ΙΩΑ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[..]ΗΣ</span></span><span data-text=\"μον\n                    αχὸς\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"μοναχός\">ΜΟΝ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[...]Σ</span><span data-text=\"ὁ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">Ο</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Με\n                    νουθ\"><span data-text=\"Με\n                    νουθ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Μενουθ\">ΜΕ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[...]Θ</span></span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. ΚῈΤΕκὲτε</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Ένθάδε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κὲτε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΕΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"Ἰωάννης\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἰωάννης\">ΙΩΑΝΝΗΣ</span><span data-text=\"μοναχὸς\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"μοναχός\">ΜΟΝΑΧΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"ὁ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">Ο</span><span data-text=\"Μενουθ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Μενουθ\">ΜΕΝΟΥΘ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003454_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003454_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003454.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003454-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Rizzone 2009</span>  </span></li><li><span class=\"5\">5: μαν<span>Rizzone 2009 suggests as alternative</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3673-587X\">Maria Barbieri</a></p>  <p>Qui giace Iohannes monaco, Menouth (o Mamanth).</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3673-587X\">Maria Barbieri</a></p>  <p>Here lies Iohannes Menouth (or Mamanth), the monk.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The text of Cordano 2005 / 2014 is misleading (and the suggestion that the text is in a mixture of Greek and Latin is clearly incorrect), and the edition of Rizzone is to be preferred.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 2009.0439 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a>  </li><li> 59.1110 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Cordano 2005 125 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002668\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002668</a>  </li><li> Rizzone 2009 431-434 no.2 fig.3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001634\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001634</a>  </li><li> Cordano 2014 109 no.11 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001366\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001366</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-5  130  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
